Package net.jordaria.entity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CurrencyHolder
    An interface for an entity which has currency and allows for transactions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Direction
    An angle from one to 360 which contains methods for modifying the angle.
    Entity
    An abstract entity class containing variables and methods used by all entity subclasses.
    EntityItem
    An item that has been dropped.
    EntityLiving
    An subclass of EntityWithInventory with health and a name.
    EntityNPC
    A subclass of EntityLiving
    EntityPlayer
    A subclass of EntityLiving that contains a username.
    EntityWithInventory
    A subclass of Entity that contains an inventory.
    Inventory
    Contains slots for items and methods for modifying the contents.
    InventorySlot
    A slot for an ItemStack.
